                  'sc', 'sod', 'pot', 'hemo',

kdata
names <- names(kdata)
for (name in names[-1])
{
  if (name %in% c('age','bp', 'su', 'bgr', 'bu',
                  'sc', 'sod', 'pot', 'hemo',
                  'pcv', 'wbcc', 'rbcc')){
    print(
    ggplot(data = kdata) +
     geom_histogram(mapping = aes_(x = as.name(name), fill = substitute(class)))
          )
  }
  else{
    print(
    ggplot(data = kdata) +
     geom_bar(mapping = aes_(x = as.name(name), fill = substitute(class))
              )
    )
  }
}
